                       Welcome to RelayBot
               A simple multi-protocol chat relay bot.

DESCRIPTION:
This program is designed as a simple in game chat relay service. It is
currently capable of relaying IRC messages and Minecraft chat messages.

REQUIREMENTS:
Requires at the very least Python 2.6 (as far as I know)

INSTALLATION:
Installation is simple, once downloaded you need only copy exampleconfig.xml
to config.xml, read the enclosed comments and configure as necesary.
After completing config.xml you will then be able to run the bot using
'python run.py'
